name: Lisa Brown
description: I am self-confident, mature but still young lady who is looking for one thing only deep love, warm, passionate, tender, naughty but real love that will make me completely happy! I have a very open and lively personality, I like to stay active, I enjoy meeting friends. I like to take care of my appearance but I value inner beauty as well. I have a serious goal – long lasting and strong relationship. You won’t regret for giving me a chance to enter your life.
